  "data": {
    "title": "Formstack Tips: Best Ways to Automate Forms & Workflows",
    "excerpt": "Discover the best ways to use Formstack for automating forms, documents, and e-signatures. These tips will save your team hours every week.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/formstack-tips.jpg",
        "alt": "Formstack Tips: Best Ways to Automate Forms & Workflows",
        "filename": "formstack-tips.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you've ever stared at a spreadsheet full of form submissions and thought \"there has to be a better way,\" you're right. Formstack is that better way — and I'm going to show you exactly how to squeeze every drop of value out of it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've spent serious time with Formstack's platform, from basic form creation to their full Suite offering. What follows isn't theory. These are real, actionable tips that will transform how your team handles data collection, document generation, and signatures.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Makes Formstack Stand Out",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-formstack"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack isn't just another form builder. It's a complete ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "workflow automation platform",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that handles three critical business processes in one place:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Digital forms",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " with conditional logic, calculations, and integrations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Document generation",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that auto-populates templates with form data",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "E-signatures",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that eliminate the print-sign-scan dance entirely",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The magic happens when you chain these together. A client fills out one form, and Formstack generates a contract, sends it for signature, and files the completed document — all without anyone touching a keyboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's a concrete example: A consulting firm I know uses Formstack to onboard new clients. Before, it took 45 minutes of admin work per client. Now? The client fills out a single form, and everything else happens automatically. They onboard 3x more clients without hiring anyone.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip #1: Start with Smart Forms, Not Blank Pages",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The biggest mistake new users make is building forms from scratch. Formstack has dozens of pre-built templates designed for specific industries and use cases.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what I recommend:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Browse the template library first",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Pick one close to your needs",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Customize from there",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The conditional logic feature is where things get powerful. You can show or hide fields based on previous answers. For example, if someone selects \"Yes\" to having insurance, the next three fields about insurance details appear. If they select \"No,\" those fields stay hidden.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This keeps forms clean and relevant. Users only see what applies to them, which dramatically increases completion rates.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pro tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Use the multi-page form feature for longer surveys. Breaking a 30-question form into three pages of 10 questions feels way less intimidating to respondents.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip #2: Automate Document Generation",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://intellistack.partnerlinks.io/mhua7fhknizd"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is the feature that made me fall in love with ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Document generation lets you create templates that automatically fill with data from your forms. Think proposals, contracts, invoices, onboarding packets — anything you currently create manually by copying and pasting form responses into Word docs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How to set it up:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Upload your existing document template (Word or PDF)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Map form fields to placeholders in the document",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Connect a form to the template",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Trigger generation on form submission",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A real estate agency uses this for lease agreements. Tenants fill out an application form, and Formstack generates a complete lease document with all their details pre-filled. The leasing agent reviews it, sends it for e-signature, and the deal closes in hours instead of days.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/formstack-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "new features rolling out this year",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " make document generation even smoother with better formatting options and faster processing.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip #3: Build Workflows That Run Themselves",
