        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Formstack free to use?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack offers a free trial so you can test all features before committing. Paid plans start at $83/month for Forms (billed annually). The Suite plan, which includes documents and e-signatures, is available at a higher tier. Annual billing saves you two months compared to monthly pricing.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Formstack replace DocuSign for e-signatures?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, Formstack's built-in e-signature feature handles most business signing needs. It's legally compliant with ESIGN and UETA, includes audit trails, supports multiple signers with defined order, and works on mobile devices. Many teams consolidate their form builder and e-signature tool into Formstack to reduce software costs and simplify workflows.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What integrations does Formstack support?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Formstack integrates with 250+ tools including Salesforce, Google Sheets, Slack, Stripe, HubSpot, Microsoft 365, and many more. You can also connect it to thousands of additional apps through Zapier. The Salesforce integration is particularly powerful, allowing you to push form data directly into leads, contacts, or custom objects.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Formstack HIPAA compliant?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, Formstack offers HIPAA-compliant features for healthcare organizations. This includes secure data collection, encrypted storage, and BAA (Business Associate Agreement) availability. Healthcare teams use it for patient intake forms, medical history questionnaires, and consent documentation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
